snippet.title: Season Five ‘Last Stand' Cinematic | Call of Duty: Warzone
snippet.description:
Legends never die – and that includes legendary villains 😈

Things are heating up and it's time to choose your side in the free 'Last Stand' content update in #Vanguard and #Warzone 🔥
